  "body": "## Summary\n\n- **Real MXG roadmap data** — replaced LeanIX placeholders with 25 live Signavio MXG features from the ProductBoard M&C external+internal board (CSV export 2026-05-05), grouped across Legacy Process Manager, Suite Repository, and Process Modeler\n- **JS syntax fix** — repaired critical U+2019 smart-quote bug in `ROADMAP_DATA` that silently broke the entire Roadmap tab (Roadmap tab was rendering blank)\n- **MxC Assistant chatbot** — fully client-side chat widget (no API key required) that answers questions about skills, roadmap, and the portal using the embedded `SKILLS_DATA`, `ROADMAP_DATA`, and `FAQ_DATA` arrays\n- **Portal metadata** — OG description corrected (57 skills to 50 skills), `lastUpdated` updated to 2026-05-05\n\n## Roadmap now — 25 MXG features\n\n| Area | NOW | NEXT | LATER |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| Legacy Process Manager | 1 | 2 | 4 |\n| Suite Repository | 3 | 1 | 5 |\n| Process Modeler | 5 | 1 | 3 |\n\nData source: M&C-external-+-internal.csv (ProductBoard board export, 2026-05-05). Teams: Process Guardians, Roots, The Sims, Dictionary, Process Pioneers, Process Vanguards, Kestrel.\n\n## Chatbot capabilities\n\n- Skill name lookup with fuzzy word scoring (all 50 skills + 8 scenarios)\n- Category browse (8 categories: Process & BPMN, Analytics & Insights, Planning & Backlog, Documents & Delivery, Communication, Strategy & Coaching, SPM Knowledge, Productivity)\n- Roadmap queries by area or status (NOW / NEXT / LATER)\n- FAQ keyword matching (12 Q&A pairs)\n- 6 quick-reply chips on open for common questions\n- Graceful fallback with suggested queries\n\n## Test plan\n\n- [ ] Roadmap tab loads and shows 3 area columns with NOW/NEXT/LATER entries (was blank before the quote fix)\n- [ ] Chat bubble appears bottom-right corner; clicking opens the panel\n- [ ] Chat: type \"what is now\" — returns 9 in-progress features with area labels\n- [ ] Chat: type \"bpmn annotator\" — returns skill description and command\n- [ ] Chat: type \"suite repository roadmap\" — returns grouped features for that area\n- [ ] Skill cards with ProductBoard links show the \"PB arrow\" badge\n- [ ] Roadmap items with insightsCount show the PB insights badge\n- [ ] `docs/MxC/mxc-skills.html` and `marketplace/MxC/mxc-skills.html` are byte-for-byte identical",
